

### What does the code?
Lets you draw moving up|down|left|righ pressing W|S|A|D
Each user that connects to the app via browser will get a new color to draw
and he/she could see what other users are drawing from that moment.


### To run the code

#Install necessary packages
sudo apt-get install build-essential libssl-dev 

#Install node [http://nodejs.org/]
wget http://nodejs.org/dist/v0.6.6/node-v0.6.6.tar.gz
tar xvzf node-v0.6.6.tar.gz
cd node-v0.6.6/
./configure
make
sudo make install

#Install curl
sudo apt-get install curl

#Install npm
sudo curl http://npmjs.org/install.sh | sudo sh

#Install socket.i[http://socket.io/#how-to-use]
 (Do it after cloning the project, in the root dir of proy1)
npm -d install socket.io

#Change the ip in index.html

#Run the app
node app.js

#Go to the browser, type your ip address, port 8080


